        <abstract>
            <p>Asks for a pea variety for an experiment.</p> 
<p>Discusses C. F. v. Gärtner’s results [in <hi rend="italic">Bastarderzeugung im Pflanzenreich</hi> (1849)]. Criticises Gärtner’s belief that hybrids are always less fertile than their parents.</p> 
            <p>Asks about MJB’s experiments.</p>
        </abstract>
